<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/19723850" target="_blank" data-id="69635" data-za-element-name="Title">
好的 Web 前端年薪会有多少？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/19723850/answer/14015533">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="726231">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="14015533"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>173</a>
</div>

