<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/35133714" target="_blank" data-id="6260166" data-za-element-name="Title">
什么样的前端才是大公司要的前端？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/35133714/answer/61570470">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="20040910">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="61570470"> -->

