<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/31263616" target="_blank" data-id="4688130" data-za-element-name="Title">
自学前端应该怎么制定循序渐进的学习计划，看书和实践应该怎么分配呢？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/31263616/answer/51512618">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="16008218">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="51512618"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>171</a>
